<body class="focus-connected">
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Interactive Unit Circle & Hyperbola</h1>
            <p>Explore the profound connection between circular and hyperbolic trigonometry. Drag the point on the circle or use the controls to see how <code class="connection-highlight">sec(θ) = cosh(p)</code> and <code class="connection-highlight green">tan(θ) = sinh(p)</code>.</p>
        </header>

        <main>
            <div class="layout-grid">
                <figure class="visualization-container">
                    <svg id="geometry-svg" viewBox="-3 -3 6 6" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke" tabindex="0" aria-label="Interactive Diagram. Use arrow keys to adjust the angle.">
                        <title>Unit Circle and Hyperbola Visualization</title>
                        <desc>An interactive diagram where a changing angle θ on a unit circle controls a point on a unit hyperbola. Lines representing sec(θ) and cosh(p) are shown to be equal, as are tan(θ) and sinh(p). The corresponding circular and hyperbolic sector areas are also visualized.</desc>

                        <defs>
                            <marker id="arrowhead" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="5" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse" fill="var(--text-muted-color)">
                                <path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" />
                            </marker>
                        </defs>

                        <rect class="svg-bg" x="-3" y="-3" width="6" height="6" />
                        <g id="svg-grid"></g>
                        <path id="svg-unit-hyperbola" class="svg-unit-hyperbola hyperbolic-element"></path>
                        <circle class="svg-unit-circle circular-element" cx="0" cy="0" r="1" />

                        <line class="svg-axis" x1="-3" y1="0" x2="3" y2="0" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)" />
                        <line class="svg-axis" x1="0" y1="3" x2="0" y2="-3" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)" />

                        <g id="svg-axis-labels" text-anchor="middle" font-size="0.12px" fill="var(--text-muted-color)">
                            <text class="svg-axis-label" x="1" y="-0.15">1</text><text class="svg-axis-label" x="2" y="-0.15">2</text>
                            <text class="svg-axis-label" x="-1" y="-0.15">-1</text><text class="svg-axis-label" x="-2" y="-0.15">-2</text>
                            <text class="svg-axis-label" x="-0.15" y="-1" dominant-baseline="central">1</text><text class="svg-axis-label" x="-0.15" y="-2" dominant-baseline="central">2</text>
                            <text class="svg-axis-label" x="-0.15" y="1" dominant-baseline="central">-1</text><text class="svg-axis-label" x="-0.15" y="2" dominant-baseline="central">-2</text>
                        </g>

                        <g id="svg-dynamic-elements">
                            <path id="svg-arc-theta" class="svg-arc-theta circular-element" data-highlight="area-circ-group"></path>
                            <path id="svg-area-hyperbolic" class="svg-area-hyperbolic hyperbolic-element" data-highlight="area-hyper-group"></path>

                            <line id="svg-guideline-radial" class="svg-guideline" />
                            <line id="svg-guideline-tan" class="svg-guideline circular-element" />
                            <line id="svg-guideline-hyperbola" class="svg-guideline" />

                            <path id="svg-projection-radial" class="svg-projection-line"></path>
                            <path id="svg-projection-horizontal" class="svg-projection-line"></path>

                            <line id="svg-line-cos" class="svg-dynamic-line svg-line-cos circular-element" data-highlight="cos-group" />
                            <line id="svg-line-sin" class="svg-dynamic-line svg-line-sin circular-element" data-highlight="sin-group" />
                            <line id="svg-line-tan-sinh" class="svg-dynamic-line svg-line-tan-sinh" data-highlight="tan-sinh-group" />
                            <line id="svg-line-sec-cosh" class="svg-dynamic-line svg-line-sec-cosh" data-highlight="sec-cosh-group" />

                            <circle id="svg-point-circle" class="svg-point circular-element" />
                            <circle id="svg-point-tangent" class="svg-point circular-element" />
                            <circle id="svg-point-hyperbola" class="svg-point hyperbolic-element" />

                            <text id="svg-label-theta" class="svg-label svg-label-theta circular-element" text-anchor="middle">θ</text>
                            <text id="svg-label-cos" class="svg-label svg-label-cos circular-element" text-anchor="middle">cos</text>
                            <text id="svg-label-sin" class="svg-label svg-label-sin circular-element" text-anchor="middle">sin</text>
                            <text id="svg-label-tan-sinh" class="svg-label svg-label-tan-sinh" text-anchor="start">tan=sinh</text>
                            <text id="svg-label-sec-cosh" class="svg-label svg-label-sec-cosh" text-anchor="middle">sec=cosh</text>
                        </g>
                    </svg>
                    <figcaption id="viz-caption">Drag the point on the circle, or use the controls. Select the diagram and use arrow keys for precise control.</figcaption>
                </figure>

                <aside class="sidebar">
                    <section class="panel controls-panel" aria-labelledby="controls-heading">
                        <h2 id="controls-heading">Controls</h2>
                        <div class="controls-group">
                            <div class="control-item">
                                <label for="angle-slider">Angle (θ)</label>
                                <div class="angle-input-wrapper">
                                    <input type="number" id="angle-input" value="45.0" min="-89.9" max="89.9" step="0.1" aria-label="Precise angle in degrees">
                                    <input type="range" id="angle-slider" name="angle" min="-89.9" max="89.9" value="45" step="0.1" aria-label="Angle slider">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="control-item">
                                <label id="focus-mode-label">Focus Mode</label>
                                <div class="focus-mode-toggle" role="radiogroup" aria-labelledby="focus-mode-label">
                                    <button type="button" role="radio" aria-checked="true" data-mode="connected">Connected</button>
                                    <button type="button" role="radio" aria-checked="false" data-mode="circular">Circular</button>
                                    <button type="button" role="radio" aria-checked="false" data-mode="hyperbolic">Hyperbolic</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="control-item toggle-switch">
                               <label for="projection-toggle" id="projection-label">Show Geometric Projection</label>
                               <input type="checkbox" id="projection-toggle" role="switch" aria-checked="false">
                            </div>
                            <div class="control-item">
                                <label for="speed-slider">Animation Speed</label>
                                <input type="range" id="speed-slider" min="0.1" max="1.5" value="0.5" step="0.1" aria-label="Animation speed">
                            </div>
                             <button id="play-pause-btn" type="button" class="play-pause-btn" aria-label="Play animation">
                                <svg id="play-icon" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"></path></svg>
                                <svg id="pause-icon" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="display: none;" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M6 19h4V5H6v14zm8-14v14h4V5h-4z"></path></svg>
                                <span id="play-pause-text">Play</span>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <details class="panel explanation-panel" id="explanation" open>
                        <summary>What am I looking at?</summary>
                        <p>This visualization reveals the deep link between circular functions (like <code>tan</code>, <code>sec</code>) and hyperbolic functions (<code>sinh</code>, <code>cosh</code>) through the <strong>Gudermannian function</strong>.</p>
                        <p>The angle <code>θ</code> on the unit circle defines a parameter <code>p</code> on the hyperbola such that <code>sec(θ) = cosh(p)</code> and <code>tan(θ) = sinh(p)</code>. This parameter <code>p</code>, known as the hyperbolic angle, is the result of the inverse Gudermannian function applied to <code>θ</code>.</p>
                        <p>Crucially, the area of the circular sector is <code>θ/2</code>, and the area of the hyperbolic sector is <code>p/2</code>. Hover over the area values below to see the corresponding shapes highlight.</p>
                    </details>

