            .container { padding: 1rem; }
            .panel { padding: 1rem; }
            .angle-input-wrapper { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; gap: 0.5rem; }
            #angle-input { width: 100%; text-align: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="focus-connected">
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Interactive Unit Circle & Hyperbola</h1>
            <p>Explore the profound connection between circular and hyperbolic trigonometry. Drag the point on the circle or use the controls to see how <code class="connection-highlight">sec(θ) = cosh(p)</code> and <code class="connection-highlight green">tan(θ) = sinh(p)</code>.</p>
