<body class="focus-connected">
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Interactive Unit Circle & Hyperbola</h1>
            <p>Explore the profound connection between circular and hyperbolic trigonometry. Drag a point or use the controls to see how <code class="connection-highlight">sec(θ) = cosh(p)</code> and <code class="connection-highlight green">tan(θ) = sinh(p)</code>.</p>
        </header>

        <main>
            <div class="layout-grid">
                <figure class="visualization-container" aria-labelledby="viz-caption">
                    <svg id="geometry-svg" viewBox="-3 -3 6 6" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke" tabindex="0" aria-label="Interactive Diagram. Use arrow keys to adjust the angle.">
                        <title>Unit Circle and Hyperbola Visualization</title>
                        <desc>An interactive diagram where a changing angle θ on a unit circle corresponds to a parameter p on a unit hyperbola. Lines representing sec(θ) and cosh(p) are shown to be equal, as are tan(θ) and sinh(p). The relationship can be explored by dragging either the circle point or the hyperbola point.</desc>

                        <defs>
                            <marker id="arrowhead" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="5" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse" fill="var(--text-muted-color)">
                                <path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" />
                            </marker>
                        </defs>

                        <rect class="svg-bg" x="-3" y="-3" width="6" height="6" />
                        <g id="svg-grid"></g>
                        <path id="svg-unit-hyperbola" class="svg-unit-hyperbola hyperbolic-element"></path>
                        <circle class="svg-unit-circle circular-element" cx="0" cy="0" r="1" />

                        <line class="svg-axis" x1="-3" y1="0" x2="3" y2="0" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)" />
                        <line class="svg-axis" x1="0" y1="3" x2="0" y2="-3" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)" />

                        <g id="svg-axis-labels" text-anchor="middle">
                            <text class="svg-axis-label" x="1" y="-0.15">1</text><text class="svg-axis-label" x="2" y="-0.15">2</text>
                            <text class="svg-axis-label" x="-1" y="-0.15">-1</text><text class="svg-axis-label" x="-2" y="-0.15">-2</text>
                            <text class="svg-axis-label" x="-0.15" y="-1" dominant-baseline="central">1</text><text class="svg-axis-label" x="-0.15" y="-2" dominant-baseline="central">2</text>
                            <text class="svg-axis-label" x="-0.15" y="1" dominant-baseline="central">-1</text><text class="svg-axis-label" x="-0.15" y="2" dominant-baseline="central">-2</text>
                        </g>

                        <g id="svg-dynamic-elements">
                            <path id="svg-arc-theta" class="svg-arc-theta circular-element" data-highlight="area-circ-group"></path>
                            <path id="svg-area-hyperbolic" class="svg-area-hyperbolic hyperbolic-element" data-highlight="area-hyper-group"></path>

                            <line id="svg-guideline-radial" class="svg-guideline" />
                            <line id="svg-guideline-tan" class="svg-guideline circular-element" />
                            <line id="svg-guideline-hyperbola" class="svg-guideline" />

